---
import {Markdown} from 'astro/components'
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Title from '@components/Title.astro'
import Image from '@components/Image.astro'
import BackToTop from '@components/BackToTop.astro'

import sponsors from '@data/sponsors.json'
---

<BaseLayout title="Supporters">
	<!-- INTRO -->
	<section class="content-container mb-4 sm:mb-6">
		<p class="content">
			Your tax-deductible contribution will help to pay for the many expenses and logistics associated with this amazing event as well as outreach programming throughout the year. Financial support or in-kind contributions from businesses and community members are the backbone of our success.
			<br/><br/>
			For more information about sponsorship opportunities please contact us at:
			<br/>
			<a href="mailto:fundraising@honkfestwest.org" >fundraising@honkfestwest.org</a>
		</p>
	</section>

	<div class="flex flex-wrap lg:flex-nowrap gap-4 sm:gap-6">
		<div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:gap-6">

			<!-- READY TO PARTICIPATE? -->
			<section class="content-container">
				<Title title="Ready to Participate?"/>
				<p class="content">
					<Markdown>
						HONK! Festival West is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization. 
						<br/><br/>
						Tax ID #86-3761255. 
						<br/><br/>
						Donations to HONK! Festival West are tax-deductible to the extent allowed by law. 
						<br/><br/>
						Donations can be made via check to:
						<span class="flex flex-col block mt-2 font-bold">
							HONK! Festival West
							<br/>
							PO Box 20242
							<br/>
							Seattle, WA 98102
						</span>
						<br/>
						Or securely at:
						<br/>
						<a href="https://connect.clickandpledge.com/w/Form/a6086a7f-ef18-4eb8-a2bc-ffa205759fcc" class="block transition ease-in-out hover:bg-main-color-300 hover:bg-opacity-20 py-1 px-4 mt-2 text-center rounded-full border-4 border-main-color-300 border-opacity-80 hover:border-opacity-100 w-auto">
							<span class="block text-lg content hover:text-white">Click & Pledge</span>
						</a>
					</Markdown>
				</p>
			</section>
		</div>
		<div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:gap-6">
			<section class="content-container">
				<BackToTop />
				<Title title="Supporters"/>
				<p class="content">
					<Markdown>
						This project is supported in part by the [National Endowment for the Arts](https://www.arts.gov/) and the [WA State Arts Commission](https://www.arts.wa.gov/).
					</Markdown>
					<span class="block grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 sm:gap-10 sm:flex-nowrap mt-2 sm:mb-5">

						<a class="block mb-3 sm:mb-0" href={sponsors.nea.link} >
							<Image 
								className="w-auto rounded bg-white p-2" 
								src={sponsors.nea.image} alt={sponsors.nea.name}
								tr={sponsors.nea.tr}
							/>
						</a>	
						<a class="block mb-3 sm:mb-0" href={sponsors.artswa.link} >
							<Image 
								className="w-auto rounded bg-white p-2" 
								src={sponsors.artswa.image} alt={sponsors.artswa.name}
								tr={sponsors.artswa.tr}
							/>
						</a>
					</span>
					<span class="border-b-4 border-opacity-60 border-title-primary-color border-dotted w-full block mb-4"/>

					<Markdown>
						HONK! Festival West is supported by grants from [4Culture](http://www.4culture.org/), 
						 [Arts Fund](https://www.artsfund.org/), and [King County CREATIVE](https://kingcountycreative.com/).
					</Markdown>
					<span class="block grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 sm:gap-10 sm:flex-nowrap mt-2 sm:mb-5">
						{sponsors.arts.map((sponsor) => (
							<a class="block mb-3 sm:mb-0" href={sponsor.link} >
								<Image 
									className="w-auto rounded bg-white p-2" 
									src={sponsor.image} alt={sponsor.name}
									tr={sponsor.tr}
								/>
							</a>	
						))}
					</span>

					<span class="border-b-4 border-opacity-60 border-title-primary-color border-dotted w-full block mb-4"/>

					<Markdown>
						Thank you to our partner organizations for their support in building a thriving creative community in Seattle:
					</Markdown>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-2 sm:gap-10 sm:flex-nowrap mt-2 sm:mb-5">
						{sponsors.shoutouts.map((sponsor) => (
							<a class="block  h-16 lg:h-32 mb-3 sm:mb-0" href={sponsor.link} >
								<Image 
									className="w-auto rounded bg-white p-1" 
									src={sponsor.image} alt={sponsor.name}
									tr={sponsor.tr}
								/>
							</a>	
						))}
					</div>

					<span class="border-b-4 border-opacity-60 border-title-primary-color border-dotted w-full block mb-4"/>

					<Markdown>
						We thank the original [HONK! festival](http://honkfest.org/)—the mothership—which inspired our festival and has since seen other offspring arise in Austin, Detroit, Australia, Brazil and beyond!
					</Markdown>
				</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>